reviewText: I do love Daniel Tosh's skewed humor!  "Oh no he didn't" is frequently uttered while watching his show.  But I can't stop watching!  I came to Tosh. 0 in 2012 so it's kinda cool to see these early shows and how the program has evolved.  Good stuff!

This mixed season DVD offers a lot of laughs. However, it seems like Tosh hasn't quite caught lightening in a bottle here like he did with the first and second installments. This product is worth seeing just not the 1-2 punch I was hoping for.
If you liove tosh.o then this is a must have.  Looking forward to the many more seasons that will be to come

For those wondering, this "volume 3" set is only available on dvd and collects the last 6 episodes of season 1 and the first 9 episodes of season 2, which bridges the gap between the already available volume 1 & 2 sets. It is a Wal-Mart exclusive and retails for around $20. You can find more info here: <...>

I really like Tosh. 0 as a comedian and this duel season combo is a great add to my collection of his TV show.
